  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Insatsen syftar till att slutf&#xF6;ra etablering av African Risk Capaciy (ARC), inklusive instutionalisera Agencys och dess sekretariats funktioner; bilda och kapitalisera f&#xF6;rs&#xE4;kringsbolaget  ARC Ltd,; hantera kapacitetsuppbyggnadsprogrammet i varje kandidatland i syfte att f&#xF6;rb&#xE4;ttra riskhanteringssystem, inklusive anpassa Afrika RiskView (ARV) v&#xE4;derprogramvaran, v&#xE4;lja risk&#xF6;verf&#xF6;ringsparametrar, och utveckla beredskapsplaner och s&#xE4;kerst&#xE4;lla deras kvalitet.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This intervention aims (valued at 49 million SEK) to complete the establishmnent of ARC, including instutionalising the functions of the Agency and its Secretariat, establishing and capitalising ARC Ltd, the insurance company, and managing the national-level multi-stakeholder capacity building programme in each candidate country with the aim of improving risk management systems, including customising Africa RiskView weather risk quantification software, selecting risk transfer parameters, and developing drought-response contingency plans lined to an ARC payout.</narrative>
  </description>
